description "Atton 'Jaq' Rand 

Pure Pazaak

^2Weaponry:
- Heavy Melee
- Atton's Armament (Saber)
-- Saber/Blaster Defense (0)
-- Blaster Deflect (1)
> Lightsaber (Yellow)
-- 45% less Dmg
> Echani Melee (Dual/Cyan)
-- 100% more Kb
-- 65/33% less Dmg
-- 50% less Reach

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (2)
- Absorb (1)
- Protect (2) ^3[CS4]

^8Attributes:
- Healing (2)
-- Fighting Spirit: 3/.34s to 25
- Intuition (Passive Sense 1)
- Sense Immunity
- Force Block (1)
- Getup (3)

^3Abilities:
- Poison Darts (2) ^3[CS1 Melee]
- Limited Dex Roll ^3[CS2]"